---
layout: default
title: More Info
description: Deep dives into HSC operations. What we use in the field, how we handle emergencies, our tools, our methods—transparency into how professional street care actually works.
---

<section class="archive-section">
  <div class="container">

    <div class="section-header">
      <span class="section-tag mono">// MORE INFO</span>
      <h1>More Info: Inside HSC Operations</h1>
      <p class="section-intro">Deep context on our methods, tools, and how we handle real situations on the street. Transparency into professional street-level care.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="posts-grid">
      {% for page in site.more_info %}
      <article class="post-card">
        {% if page.category %}
        <div class="post-card-meta">
          <span class="post-card-category mono">{{ page.category }}</span>
        </div>
        {% endif %}
        <h3 class="post-card-title">
          <a href="{{ page.url }}">{{ page.title }}</a>
        </h3>
        <p class="post-card-excerpt">{{ page.excerpt | strip_html | truncatewords: 25 }}</p>
        <a href="{{ page.url }}" class="post-card-link">Read more →</a>
      </article>
      {% endfor %}
    </div>

    {% if site.more_info.size == 0 %}
    <div class="empty-state">
      <p class="mono">No guides yet. Check back soon for operational details.</p>
    </div>
    {% endif %}

  </div>
</section>
